reviewText:
Q: How do you extend 30 minutes of footage to a full hour?
A: Play it half speed!

This era of Vivid productions are notorious for this very thing, and this one is just as bad if not worse than the others. In the end you get a lot of super-slo-mo and repeated fragments of shots. This is staged footage from a strip club in Hawaii from the mid '90s, so you've got a lot of cheap breast implants and flat butts, but also fantastic pubic hair (neatly trimmed). And there are a couple of naturally big-busted strippers in the group, so that's good. LaToya is a throwaway and you won't want any more of her than you get--couldn't we all have dealt with less?

No explicit nudity here, even though other Vivid stripping videos do have that.
